name: Dark Arches
description:
Traveling down this paved footpath in Warwickshire, England, you briefly emerge from a darkened gatehouse into the sunlight, only to be confronted by the darkness of the forest canopy. The stone archway invites you to step out into the daylight, but the wooded arch beyond seems a bit less welcoming.

#4 in the "Inviting You Through" series, a collection of windows, archways, and covered passages, which will invite you to look or travel through them, to see what's on the other side, or simply enjoy the journey of getting there.

35 mm film, circa 2002.
